snippet.title: Farming Simulator 19 – Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Farming Simulator 19 is out now on PS4, Xbox One, PC and Mac!

Farm like never before in the biggest and best Farming Simulator game ever, packed with new vehicles, activities, crops, animals and tools - solo or with friends.

Get it now: https://farming-simulator.com/store.php?game=fs19 


► Website: http://www.farming-simulator.com/ 
► Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/giants.farming.simulator 
► Twitter: https://twitter.com/farmingsim
► Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/giantsfarmingsimulator/
► Get Farming Simulator 19 now on the official shop: https://www.farming-simulator.com/store.php
